              <h3 class="title">

               </a>
              </h3>
             </header>

            <div class="info">
             <header class="info-header">
              <h3 class="title">
               <a href="/news/gop-us-rep-tom-reed-to-retire-after-sexual-misconduct-accusation">
                GOP US Rep. Tom Reed to retire after sexual misconduct accusation
               </a>
              </h3>
             </header>
             <p class="dek">
              U.S. Rep. Tom Reed, a Republican from western New York who was accused last week of rubbing a female lobbyists back and unhooking her bra without her consent in 2017, apologized to the woman on Sunday and announced that he will not run for reelection next year.
             </p>
             <time class="time" datetime="2021-03-21T18:26:39-07:00">
              5 hours ago
             </time>
             <!-- -->
            </div>
           </article>

                Family of woman shot, killed in Compton calls for possible hate crime investigation
               </a>
              </h3>
             </header>
             <p class="dek">

               </a>
              </h3>
             </header>

             <header class="info-header">
              <h3 class="title">
               <a href="/news/republican-congressman-apologizes-for-touching-woman-unhooking-her-bra">
                Republican congressman apologizes for touching woman, unhooking her bra
               </a>
              </h3>
             </header>
             <p class="dek">
              Nicolette Davis was 25 when Rep. Tom Reed unhooked her bra and touched her thigh at a bar in Minneapolis. "A drunk congressman is rubbing my back," she texted a co-worker. "HELP HELP." Reed now blames alcohol.
             </p>
             <time class="time" datetime="2021-03-21T18:05:20-07:00">
              5 hours ago
             </time>
